      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been well-cared for, making it a perfect choice for your next adventure. While you'll find some minor, expected signs of wear from its time on the road, it remains a sharp-looking and smooth-driving car that is ready for many more miles. It's a solid, honest vehicle that offers great value and performance!",
