      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently maintained in showroom condition. This vehicle exhibits a flawless aesthetic profile, from its unblemished exterior finish to a cabin that retains its original factory integrity. Mechanically superlative and meticulously curated, this unit represents a rare acquisition opportunity for the most discerning enthusiast. Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence in a vehicle that transcends the standard pre-owned market.",
      "price": 43500.0,
